text: In usses drihtnes noman Hælendes Cristes, ic Oswald arcebiscop mid geþafunge & leafe þæs arwyrðan hiredes on Wiogernaceastre ge iunges ge aldes gebocie sumne dæl landes minum holdan & getriowan þegne þæm is Eadric noma on twam stowum þriora hida landes on twera monna dæg twa on Tætlintune & ane æt Nioweboldan & þæt inlond þærto þe Leofinc hædde for his eadmodre hersumnesse.
Þæt is þæt he hæbbe & wel bruce his dæg & æfter his dæg anum erfewarde þæm þe him leofest se & him to gearnian wille.
& he hit hæbbe to frion ælces þingces butan geweorce & brycggeworce & ferdsocne.
Þis wæs gedon þu geare þe agan wæs fron Cristes gebyrdtide nigon hund wintra & an & hundnigonti wintra on þara broðra gewitnesse þe hiora naman her beneoðan awritene standað.
Ic Oswald ercebiscop mid Cristes rode tacne þas sylene gefestnade.
